==English==

===Noun===
'''ceasefire'''
# In [[warfare]], an [[agreed]] end to [[hostilities]] for a specific [[purpose]].  (Might only be temporary)
#: The [[rebels]] agreed to a ceasefire while the peace talks were underway.

====Synonyms====
* [[armistice]]
* [[truce]]

